<h1>Cookie Policy</h1>

<p>
  This website (<a href="https://angelomeniconi.co.uk">angelomeniconi.co.uk</a>) uses cookies to enhance your experience and track usage via Google Analytics. This policy explains what cookies are used, why, and your choices.
</p>

<section class="cookies-used">
  <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site remember preferences and provide insights about how visitors interact with the site.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>
  <ul class="cookies-grid">
    <li><code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>, <code>_gat</code> – Tracks site usage and events (Analytics / Non-essential, provided by Google)</li>
    <li><code>Other first-party cookies</code> – Remember site preferences (Functional / Essential, provided by angelomeniconi.co.uk)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why We Use Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are used to understand how visitors interact with the site, improve content and performance, and measure event tracking for analytics purposes.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Accept or reject non-essential cookies via the cookie banner on first visit.</li>
    <li>Delete cookies via your browser settings at any time.</li>
    <li>Blocking analytics may reduce the accuracy of usage statistics.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    For more information, see our <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>
</section>
